    Title: Svetâsvatara Upanishad
    Locus: IV 17
Tags:
  - Discernment-Truth=The Eye Of Eternity-Supreme Center=The Eye of the Heart
Format: verse
---
That God, the All-worker, the Great Self (imahâtman),
Ever seated in the heart of creatures,
Is framed by the heart, by the thought, by the mind --
They who know That, become immortal.
